  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Snail Quest is a puzzle game based on the 2048 movement mode.</h2><br>When the Player Input the Movement Direction.<br>Every snail will move towards the same direction and only stop when it encounters an obstacle.<br>But when the snails meet each other，they will merge into a higher level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/d6804c5c23550a2dad89016f7d3104c5.poster.avif?t=1656478253\" width=424 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/d6804c5c23550a2dad89016f7d3104c5.webm?t=1656478253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/d6804c5c23550a2dad89016f7d3104c5.mp4?t=1656478253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use the characteristics of snails to reach the designated camp.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/5d53f0ca95906ed9b75237e285d1131f.poster.avif?t=1656478253\" width=424 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/5d53f0ca95906ed9b75237e285d1131f.webm?t=1656478253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/5d53f0ca95906ed9b75237e285d1131f.mp4?t=1656478253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game now has 40 handcrafted levels，and there will be another 40 levels of updates in the future.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015740/extras/c3f44ae710b73d5975660f83480ce43f.avif?t=1656478253\" width=424 height=218 /></span><br><span cla